<item>
 <title>Robert Miles - Children</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/blog/robert-miles-children</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://vse.la/images/blogi_images/3494175222_95a0b46b7a_z.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://vse.la/images/styles/thumb330/public/blogi_images/3494175222_95a0b46b7a_z.jpg?itok=p2_WMRPO&quot; width=&quot;180&quot; height=&quot;270&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Einer schließt den Himmel auf,&lt;br /&gt;
kommt die liebe Sonne raus.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&quot;Liebe, liebe Sonne&quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The feature of this music is clear words that saving the story into the music. The tune revealed straight from the first notes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The words flow into the scene playing with the actors. The words turn back into the music saying the message.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Robert Miles&lt;/strong&gt; is a contemporary producer, composer and DJ, &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Miles&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Wiki says&lt;/a&gt;. His club tracks &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hcqNRaQRUog&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;One &amp;amp; One&lt;/a&gt;&quot;, &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jJHpK0EQ93A&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Fable&lt;/a&gt;&quot; are rotating on the radio. This music is made to be a background. The message of piano keys is soft and clear. It brings ideas to be a human wider and better.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Photo: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flickr.com/photos/nymphetaminedolls/3494175222&quot;&gt;https://www.flickr.com/photos/nymphetaminedolls/3494175222&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-rubrika field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Рубрика:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/blog/akkompanement&quot;&gt;Аккомпанемент&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/blog/populyarnye-pesni&quot;&gt;Популярные песни&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-yazik field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Язык:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/yazyk/russkiy&quot;&gt;Русский&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
